Password tips

The best passwords are a combination of words or characters that are memorable only to you. To help you choose the password we use the following rules.

The password must have a minimum length of 10 characters

Your password cannot contain sequential characters e.g abc

Your password cannot contain repetitive characters (e.g aaa, 999)

Your password cannot contain a word related to this service

Your password must not have appeared in a known data breach (we will let you know if it has)
